description: We're smoking 4 NEW cigars on today's Cigar Authority: JC Newman's new Brick House "Teaser", the Origen Maduro Originals from J. Fuego, the new Inch from Ernesto Carrillo, and Room 101's Daruma. Plus we've got the GIANT list of all the new cigars coming out this year!
